    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "**Note** [CRF-1] `testutil.RoundTripperFunc` is the correct shared location for this adapter. `coderd/coderdtest/coderdtest.go:1778` has an identical unexported `roundTripper` type and already imports `testutil`; a future cleanup could replace it. `coderd/coderdtest/oidctest/idp.go:1792` has a struct-based variant (`fakeRoundTripper`) doing the same job. Production copies in `cli/root.go:1699` and `coderd/externalauth/externalauth.go:1381` cannot import a test package, so they stay unless the helper moves to a non-test location. *(Netero, Robin)*\n\n> \ud83e\udd16",
