    "body": "**Nit** [CRF-3] `srvURL` no longer refers to a server. The old code had `srv := httptest.NewServer(...)` followed by `srvURL, err := url.Parse(srv.URL)`, so the name described the server's URL. The server is gone; this is now a placeholder URL for a mocked transport. `baseURL` matches the actual role. *(Gon)*\n\n> \ud83e\udd16",
    "commit_id": "eeb6fd64aa387cc15ac6f97a86f94b9ccd449e7c",
    "created_at": "2026-06-08T11:17:35Z",
