    "body": "**Nit** [CRF-4] `xerrors.New` adds a new import when `errors.New` would do the same thing. The file already imports `\"errors\"` (line 5, used for `errors.As` below). `errors.New` is identical to `xerrors.New` since Go 1.13. *(Ging-Go)*\n\n> \ud83e\udd16",
