    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "RoundTripperFunc.RoundTrip will panic if a nil RoundTripperFunc is ever used as a Transport (e.g. Transport: testutil.RoundTripperFunc(nil)). Since this is an exported helper, it\u2019s safer to return a clear error instead of panicking.",
    "commit_id": "91e1c7944084e666f3cf343b498bd268738b37fb",
    "created_at": "2026-06-08T14:07:53Z",
    "diff_hunk": "@@ -9,6 +9,15 @@ import (\n \t\"github.com/stretchr/testify/require\"\n )\n \n+// RoundTripperFunc adapts a function to an http.RoundTripper.\n+type RoundTripperFunc func(*http.Request) (*http.Response, error)\n+\n+var _ http.RoundTripper = RoundTripperFunc(nil)\n+\n+func (f RoundTripperFunc) RoundTrip(req *http.Request) (*http.Response, error) {\n+\treturn f(req)\n+}",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/coder/coder/pull/26132#discussion_r3373832624",
